metadata.title: 2002 (May - Jun): Ichthyoplankton Survey Data in the Region Between Unimak Pass, the Shumagin Islands, and Through Shelikof Strait to Kodiak Island - R/V Miller Freeman (Cruise ID: MF2002-07)
metadata.description: To conduct an ichthyoplankton survey and process oriented studies in the region between Unimak Pass, the Shumagin Islands, and through Shelikof Strait to Kodiak Island, Alaska, to estimate the abundance of young walleye pollock larvae, their transport, and factors influencing their survival.
